OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', Cooper says ahead of
OL,5,Cpolicy reforms
OL,7,FThe Home Secretary has said migration
OL,8,F"must be properly controlled" with
OL,9,Fministers due to lay out sweeping
OL,10,Freforms to the immigration system.
OL,12,FThe skilled visa threshold will be
OL,13,Fincreased to degree-level and
OL,14,Femployers will be told they must train
OL,15,Fworkers in the UK, under plans to be
OL,16,Fpresented to Parliament on Monday.
OL,18,FYvette Cooper has blamed a push for
OL,19,Foverseas recruitment for high net
OL,20,Fmigration figures in recent years.
