OL,4,Ccontrolled', Cooper says ahead of
OL,5,Cpolicy reforms
OL,7,FThe Immigration White Paper is being
OL,8,Fpresented as part of Government
OL,9,Fefforts to reduce net migration into
OL,10,Fthe UK, with the figure reaching
OL,11,F728,000 in 2024. Net migration is the
OL,12,Fdifference between the number of
OL,13,Fpeople moving to a country and those
OL,14,Femigrating.
OL,16,FHome Secretary Ms Cooper has said
OL,17,F"migration must be properly controlled
OL,18,Fand managed so the system is fair".
