OL,4,Ccontrolled', Cooper says ahead of
OL,5,Cpolicy reforms
OL,7,FAccording to the Home Office, there
OL,8,Fwill be tighter restrictions on
OL,9,Frecruitment for jobs with skills
OL,10,Fshortages, businesses will be
OL,11,Fsupported to take on more British
OL,12,Fworkers and employers will be told to
OL,13,Fdevelop plans to train staff in the UK.
OL,15,FIn an attempt to reduce the number of
OL,16,Flow-skilled workers coming to Britain,
OL,17,Fthe skilled visa threshold will be
OL,18,Fincreased to graduate-level.
