OL,7,FOfficials will also set up a labour
OL,8,Fmarket evidence group to examine which
OL,9,Fsectors are reliant on overseas
OL,10,Fworkers.
OL,12,FMs Cooper said: "We've seen net
OL,13,Fmigration quadruple in the space of
OL,14,Fjust four years, driven especially by
OL,15,Foverseas recruitment.
OL,17,F"We inherited a failed immigration
OL,18,Fsystem where the previous government
OL,19,Freplaced free movement with a free
OL,20,Fmarket experiment.
