OL,7,F"Employers were given much greater
OL,8,Ffreedom to recruit from abroad while
OL,9,Faction on training fell.
OL,11,F"Overseas recruitment soared at the
OL,12,Fsame time as big increases in the
OL,13,Fnumber of people not working or in
OL,14,Feducation here in the UK."
OL,16,FOfficial figures show net migration
OL,17,Fhas soared since the UK left the EU in
OL,18,FJanuary 2020, reaching a record high
OL,19,Fof 903,000 in the year to June 2023
OL,20,Fbefore falling back slightly to
OL,21,F728,000 in the following year.
