OL,7,FThe Financial Times reported that
OL,8,Fmigrants will be required to wait as
OL,9,Flong as 10 years before they can apply
OL,10,Ffor indefinite leave to remain in the
OL,11,FUK, while there has also been
OL,12,Fspeculation that visa applications
OL,13,Ffrom nationalities considered most
OL,14,Flikely to overstay and claim asylum
OL,15,Fcould be restricted.
OL,17,FLabour pledged a "fair" and "properly
OL,18,Fmanaged" immigration system in their
OL,19,Felection manifesto, but the tougher
OL,20,Fapproach on immigration comes as
OL,21,Fsupport for Reform UK grows.
