OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', Cooper says ahead of
OL,5,Cpolicy reforms
OL,7,FThe party is trying to amend the
OL,8,FBorder Security, Asylum and
OL,9,FImmigration Bill, which if accepted
OL,10,Fwould give the Government the power to
OL,11,Fcap visas in line with the country's
OL,12,Fneeds, and allow them to be revoked if
OL,13,Fthe limit is exceeded.
OL,15,FThe Tories are also behind a separate
OL,16,Famendment to the same Bill which would
OL,17,Flook to disapply the Human Rights Act
OL,18,Fin asylum and deportation cases.
