OL,3,CMigration must be 'properly
OL,4,Ccontrolled', Cooper says ahead of
OL,5,Cpolicy reforms
OL,7,FResponding to the Government's White
OL,8,FPaper, shadow home secretary Chris
OL,9,FPhilp said that "fixing Britain's
OL,10,Fmigration crisis requires a new
OL,11,Fradical approach. Labour had the
OL,12,Fopportunity to do this and have
OL,13,Ffailed".
OL,15,FHe added: "If Labour were serious
OL,16,Fabout immigration, they'd back our
OL,17,Fbinding immigration cap and back our
OL,18,Fplan to repeal the entire Human Rights
OL,19,FAct from immigration matters. But they
OL,20,Fhave got no grip, no guts and no plan."
